overview:
Bringing about efficiency in business through mobile technology.

Through the spirit of innovation and R&D in blood since its inception, Weird Logics has been on a path to introduce breakthrough products based on mobile technology, one after another for hospitality, retail, lifestyle, education and finance sector.

Helping business’ leverage mobile technology, it has helped them in achieving more customer engagement with the brand as well as streamlining their operations - both generating higher ROI for the business as a result.

Through the unique and relevant enterprise level solutions for each industry, Weird Logics has tried to fill up the identified gaps, make the enterprises think ahead of time and prepare them for future.
